result.execSummary:
The defendant Dylan D. Baker was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Dylan D. Baker is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Dylan D. Baker was found guilty of Possession of THC, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(e).
